{"tid":1590140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果話陳雲料事如神，咁呢位長者簡直係未卜先知","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T23:43:05.000Z","uid":185628,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a96972edac24f37fccfe6c495daaab15afd59d59","tid":1590140,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0SVxBmqDJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW0SVxBmqDJE&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=671123b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0SVxBmqDJE</a><br />\n陳雲：十月一日民眾要高呼「天滅中共，全黨死清光」<br />\n<br />\n長者：中國共產黨&hellip;&hellip;屌屎忽！屌咗八十幾年，全國鳩頭[2]犯有雞姦死罪！<span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨&hellip;&hellip;隨街屌死自己老母！衣冠禽獸！</span>中國共產黨&hellip;&hellip;徹底滅亡！等候人道毀滅！<span style=\"color: red;\">全黨死清光</span>！殺呀！殺到爛臭屄解放軍，電腦大爆炸！時辰未到&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n（此時長者從警員手上，搶回已登記完的身分證。警員詢問長者需不需要呼喚救護車。）<br />\n<br />\n長者：毛賊神經病就有！你地就快智障喇吓！<br />\n<br />\n（警員再次詢問長者需不需要呼喚救護車。）<br />\n<br />\n長者：你需唔需要呀？柒頭皮！<br />\n<br />\n長者：毛賊神經病呀！啲毛賊神經病，睇我身份証&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n長者：無用架&hellip;&hellip;我啲咁嘅身分証呀就快唔用喇！我要發<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙通行証</span></strong>俾共產黨解放軍！爆炸呀！電腦大爆炸呀！柒頭皮！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙通行証=為所欲為tee</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n長者：吓&hellip;&hellip;你聽唔到我話咩呀&hellip;&hellip;[3]毛賊神經病呀！<br />\n<br />\n長者：我第日啟動「公」程式嘅時候[4]，我唔會再通知呢啲柒頭皮o架喇吓！呢啲冚家鏟嗱，全部都係共產黨嚟㗎！出去！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10月1日啟動「公」程式!!!!!!!!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"62f9d94cbd8db7c0d97ffbf6e5b936506f44e949","tid":1590140,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\